  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ethnic Community Sustainable Development Project in Southeast Guizhou</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project plans to directly assist 300 families in Baishui Village (in Kaitang Township, Kaili City), Guixi and Tonghe Villages (in Liangshang Township, Sansui County). The 300 families will achieve sustainable development in their communities through this project. Beef cattle, swine and meat goats will be project animals. Another 600 families will be assisted through Passing on the Gift. Totally 900 families will benefit from this project. The project participants will achieve four objectives: 1) to improve their livelihood by intensive technical training and physical inputs; 2) to achieve community harmony and cohesion by capable SHG working; 3) to achieve environment health by ecological recycle and water-saving farming; 4) To improve communities&#x2019; market access.</narrative>
  </description>
